                     <interp inst="t17920523-63-off364" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17920523-63-cd365" type="crimeDate">14th day of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17920523-63-off364 t17920523-63-cd365"></join> last, a woollen blanket value 4 s. a linen sheet value 6 s. a box great coat value 31 s. a cloth coat value 1 s. and other things, the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17920523-63-victim592" type="victimName">
